data.description: Awesome home on corner lot in established Hillbrook subdivision in Martinez! Offering over 2200 square feet, this 4 bedroom, 3 bath home is nice and spacious! Open Great Room with cathedral ceilings, wood burning fireplace and ceiling fan! Eat-in Kitchen with ample cabinet and counter space, electric range and access to the screened-in porch! Owner Suite is on main level, French door entryway, carpet, wood burning fireplace, en-suite bath complete with Jacuzzi tub and large walk-in closet and Loft area with door to upper deck overlooking backyard. Guest Bedroom on main level! Additional full bath on main level with laundry area! Upstairs you will find 2 guest bedrooms with Jack and Jill bathroom! Outside has a nice sized fenced yard with in ground vinyl pool with new liner and outbuilding for storage!  Conveniently located close to schools, shopping and Interstate! Don't miss out on this awesome home!
